[{"id":"c50772e796e0404771b396e9e8bf2943","from":"J. Epstein","from_email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to":"Lesley Groff","to_list":[{"name":"Lesley Groff","email":"lesley@nysgllc.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Re: Maps of the 98,000 acres in Northwest Florida","date":"2007-05-01T18:15:39.000Z","formatted_date":"May 1, 2007","formatted_time":"6:15 PM","body":"send more info\n\n\n----- Original Message ----\nFrom: Lesley Groff <lesley@nysgllc.com>\nTo: J. Epstein <jeeproject@yahoo.com>\nSent: Tuesday, May 1, 2007 7:53:45 AM\nSubject: FW: Maps of the 98,000 acres in Northwest Florida\n\n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \nLesley Groff\nExecutive Assistant to Jeffrey Epstein\n \n \n\n\n\n\nFrom: Sheridan Gibson [mailto:sheridan@sheridanenterprises.com] \nSent: Tuesday, May 01, 2007 9:31 AM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: RE: Maps of the 98,000 acres in Northwest Florida\n\n\nLesley, please include the attached Regional Update and St. Joe\u2019s Annual Report too please for Jeffrey.\n\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026.\nJeffrey, St. Joe would lead the world to think that there is no more available land because they own it all, which is not true.  The 98,776  acres is available and all of Panama City Beach (not owned by St. Joe) can be bought, bull dozed down and a new world created, which needs to happen.\nWhy are industry leaders are going to India , China , & Russia when they could have Northwest Florida !?  We are\n-          THE MOST BEAUTIFUL BEACHES IN NORTH AMERICA !\n-          IN AMERICA !\n-          IN FLORIDA !\nI would make a play for St. Joe as well.\nSheridan \n \n \nSheridan Gibson\n \nSheridan Enterprises, LLC\n409 N. Andalusia Ave.\nSeagrove Beach, FL 32459\nc: 850.496.2174 \nsheridan@sheridanenterprises.com\nwww.sheridanenterprises.com\n \n \n\n \n\n\n\nFrom: Lesley Groff [mailto:lesley@nysgllc.com] \nSent: Tuesday, May 01, 2007 8:54 AM\nTo: Sheridan Gibson\nSubject: RE: Maps of the 98,000 acres in Northwest Florida\n \nok\n \n \n \n \n \n \nLesley Groff\nExecutive Assistant to Jeffrey Epstein\n \n \n \n\n\n\nFrom: Sheridan Gibson [mailto:sheridan@sheridanenterprises.com] \nSent: Tuesday, May 01, 2007 8:52 AM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: Maps of the 98,000 acres in Northwest Florida\nLesley, here are the maps for the 98,776 acres in Northwest Florida .  Please include this information for Jeffrey.\n\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\nJeffrey, here are the maps of the 98,776 acres in Northwest Florida .  The owners would like to arrange a meeting on May 23rd if you are interested in purchasing this parcel.  Again, it is the only large parcel not owned by St. Joe near the new Bay County International Airport .\nI attended the 6th Annual Family Symposium in Miami this past week and made some incredible contacts in the hedge fund, private equity sector and met the allocator for the family who did the \u201cMall of America\u201d.  His name is Ira J. Perlmuter with T5 Equity Partners, LLC out of Riverdale , NY .  They are very interested in the piece, but I have not contacted them yet as I was waiting to see if you are interested first.\nI will call you this afternoon to see if you are interested.\nSheridan\nBest,\n \nNo virus found in this outgoing message.\nChecked by AVG Free Edition.\nVersion: 7.5.467 / Virus Database: 269.6.2/781 - Release Date: 4/30/2007 9:14 AM\n \nNo virus found in this outgoing message.\nChecked by AVG Free Edition.\nVersion: 7.5.467 / Virus Database: 269.6.2/781 - Release Date: 4/30/2007 9:14 AM\n\n\nNo virus found in this incoming message.\nChecked by AVG Free Edition.\nVersion: 7.5.467 / Virus Database: 269.6.2/781 - Release Date: 4/30/2007 9:14 AM\n\n\n